Interface IPassThroughSwConnector

    public interface IPassThroughSwConnector
extends IEntity, ISwConnector
    IPassThroughSwConnector: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This kind of SwConnector can be used inside a CompositionSwComponentType to connect two delegation PortPrototypes.
